('main-image-url', 'uk', 'Home Improvement', 'The URL where a main image of the product is located.  If you have child products and they do not vary in appearance in any way, you do not need to supply a value in this field for those child products.  If you have trouble uploading images in a webserver or link the URL in this template, you can first upload the product template without the images & later upload the images one by one in seller central using "Manage your Inventory" under product management.', 'Images should have 72-pixels-per-inch resolution and be 500 pixels minimum in length (on the longest side).  There cannot be any spaces or high ascii characters in the image url.  Save the image to your Web server and supply the URL to the image in this field.  Accepted formats are .jpeg, .jpg, and .gif', 'http://www.companyname.com/images/1250.main.jpg', 'Required\n\nOptional for parent products');
