('parent-child', 'uk', 'Apparel', 'Defines whether the product is a main (parent) product or a variation (child) of the main product. The "parent" defines all basic data about the product. The "child" or "children" define the possible variations (i.e., size, colour) of the parent product. The parent product is not purchasable; it simply specifies attributes of the product that are common among all of its children. Only parent attributes will be displayed on Amazon.co.uk.', 'If building a variation relationship, select one of the following options: parent or child.', 'The product "men''s polo shirt" would have the value "parent" and the product "men''s white polo shirt (XL)" would have the value "child."', ''),
('parent-child', 'uk', 'Shoes & Accessories', 'Defines whether the product is a main (parent) product or a variation (child) of the main product. The "parent" defines all basic data about the product. The "child" or "children" define the possible variations (i.e., size, colour) of the parent product. The parent product is not purchasable; it simply specifies attributes of the product that are common among all of its children. Only parent attributes will be displayed on Amazon.co.uk.', 'If building a variation relationship, select one of the following options: parent or child.', 'The product "men''s polo shirt" would have the value "parent" and the product "men''s white polo shirt (XL)" would have the value "child."', 'Optional'),
