('product_type', 'uk', 'Automotive', 'This entry defines the type of product that you''d like to list on Amazon. Select one value from the predefined list of valid values.', 'Please select one of the following values: AutoAccessoryMisc or AutoPart', 'AutoAccessoryMisc', 'Required'),
