('product_type', 'uk', 'Video Games', 'Within a category there are often multiple product types defined. For example, for the Video Games category, there are separate values for each: Video Games, Video Game Accessories and Video Game Hardware. For the  Software category, there is Software, Software Games, and Software Downloads. Each of these categories are included in this video game template workbook.', 'Input one of the following valid values: \nVideoGames\nVideaGamesHardware\nVideoGamesAccessories\nSoftware\nSoftwareGames\nSoftwareDownloads\nNote: Please see the ICG for details.', 'VideoGames', 'Required'),
