('protein', 'uk', 'Grocery & Beverages', 'The amount of protein per 100g or 100ml. Typically provided on the product packaging.\nPlease note that it is your responsibility to ensure that any information provided or selected complies with applicable laws and regulations.\n', 'A positive floating point number (decimal) with maximum digits for fraction part is 4 (for example: 1.23). Use a dot as a decimal seperator.', '5', 'Required if any nutritional information is provided.'),
