('RelationshipType', 'uk', 'Lighting', 'Describes the relationship between products that are related.\n\nIf the product is part of a variation family (i.e., a specific color of an item that is available in several colors), enter the value "Variation".\n\nEnter "Accessory" if the item should be offered on it''s own and as an accessory to another standalone item (e.g. a lightbulb as an accessory for a lamp).\n\n', 'Select one of the following options: Variation or Accessory\n\nNote: Variation relationships are not supported for LightingAccessories.', 'Variation', 'Optional\n\nRequired when column parent-sku is populated.'),
('RelationshipType', 'uk', 'Sports', 'Describes the relationship between products that are related. If the product is a variation (i.e., a different size and &gt; or color) of another product (e.g., white polo shirt" is a variation of "polo shirt"), enter the value Variation. This is the only value that can be used and must be entered only for the child items. Do not put this value in for a parent item.', 'Select one of the following options: Variation, Accessory', 'Variation', 'Optional'),
